Scroll Request (10)
Returned block contains :
  0	Window handle
  4	Visible area minimum x
  8	Visible area minimum y
  12	Visible area maximum x
  16	Visible area maximum y
  20	Scroll x offset
  24	Scroll y offset
  28	Handle to open window behind
  32	Scroll x direction
  36	Scroll y direction

Scroll directions :
  -2	Page Left/Down
  -1	Left/Down
   0
   1	Right/Up
   2	Page Right/Up

You use the scroll directions to update the scroll offsets, and then you do a <Wimp_OpenWindow>.